title: SC EP:7 Sasquatch Sounds vs Known Animal Sounds

description: In this episode we bring you some of the best Bigfoot stories, sounds and news topics. We will also be answering questions from our listeners. Do you know the difference between a reported Bigfoot sound and a known animal like a fox?
